item.description:
The Open Force Field Consortium Advisory Board met on 13 June, 2019. The minutes are summarized as follows:
The first optimized force field The aim is to have the first force field released by Sept 1 and evaluations performed by Oct 1. Specific discussion about it takes place in #release-1 channel on Slack.
Types: The same typing tree as smirnoff99Frosst will be used, but the differentiable parameters in (a subset of) torsion, valence, and Lennard-Jones parameters will be optimized;
